  "title": "Video by eshton",
  "description": "I absolutely loved the flavours here! Combining Spanish food with his own unique experience, Chef @gonzaloland serves dishes that are both homely and luxurious! \n\nMy personal favourites were of course the Beef Short Rib, which was extremely tender, and the Hokkaido Scallops with Foie Gras for those delicious umami flavours! \n\nBut one of the most interesting dishes was their own variation of paella! The Foie Gras & Fig Rice combines those rich buttery notes with perfectly al dente golden rice to create a dish that was delicious!\n\n📍 NÓMADA, 1 Keong Saik Rd., 01-05, Singapore 089109\n\n#sgfoodie #wheretoeat #sgrestaurant #datenight #paella #foiegras #shortribs #scallops #beef #eshton",
